 "lrc": "[00:00.00]Mm.\n[00:00.08]Este verano se siente diferente.\n[00:06.08]Pero esto no es vacaciones.\n[00:08.64]Esto es presión.\n[00:09.60]Esto es fuego.\n[00:13.44]Esto es cuando el vacío aprende mi nombre.\n[00:16.16]¡Construye!\n[00:16.56]¡Sube!\n[00:18.32]Pressure make gold!\n[00:19.38]La presión hace oro!\n[00:23.68]Ay ya ya\n[00:23.84]Estamos afuera now\n[00:28.48]Ay ya ya\n[00:28.48]Feet on the ground\n[00:28.80]Ay ya ya\n[00:31.60]Let the bass roll low\n[00:32.64]Del vacío hasta el oro\n[00:32.68]I had too much weight sitting heavy on my shoulders\n[00:34.72]Demasiadas noches frías, too many dreams getting older\n[00:37.12]Same walls, same clock, same fight with time\n[00:39.68]Same voice in the dark saying “you ain’t gon’ shine”\n[00:42.00]Pero el tambor sonó like a war call\n[00:44.88]Brass hit hard, made the whole block talk\n[00:47.44]One deep breath, then I stood up tall\n[00:49.52]Had to stop waiting, had to take it all\n[00:52.32]Laptop closed but the soul still loading\n[00:54.80]Hands still dirty but the heart still golden\n[00:56.96]I was down in the void where the lights don’t show\n[00:59.36]Now I beat on the dark till the whole thing glow\n[01:02.16]Yo no estaba roto\n[01:03.84]Me estaban formando\n[01:05.44]Yo no estaba muerto\n[01:08.45]Me estaban quemando\n[01:10.16]Suelta el miedo\n[01:11.88]Llena el pecho con fire\n[01:14.40]Step through the noise\n[01:15.44]Climb a little higher\n[01:16.69]No shame in the scars\n[01:18.00]No fear in the climb\n[01:19.28]Si el mundo grita duro\n[01:20.56]I’ma turn it into mine\n[01:22.16]Venimos del void\n[01:23.12]Now we turn it into gold\n[01:24.48]Oro en el pecho\n[01:26.32]Gold in the soul\n[01:27.44]Built from the pressure\n[01:29.12]Raised by the cold\n[01:29.92]Venimos del void\n[01:31.04]Now we turn it into gold\n[01:32.00]¡Oro!\n[01:32.80]But we aiming past gold!\n[01:35.36]¡Oro!\n[01:35.76]Que lo sepa todo el mundo!\n[01:41.22]Oh-oh, déjalo arder\n[01:42.96]Oh-oh, déjalo ver\n[01:43.44]Oh-oh, mírame crecer\n[01:44.08]Venimos del void\n[01:45.20]Now we turn it into gold\n[01:46.24]Mente clara\n[02:01.92]Heart bold\n[02:02.96]Manos arriba\n[02:03.68]Still gold\n[02:04.40]New me\n[02:05.44]Still loading\n[02:05.92]Alma limpia\n[02:08.32]Still glowing\n[02:10.72]De Queens to the island, de la isla to the sky\n[02:13.20]Boricua y Quisqueya, fuego in my eyes\n[02:15.84]Plátano, perico ripiao, drums in the street\n[02:18.16]808 under my chest, brass under my feet\n[02:20.48]No more waiting on permission\n[02:21.68]No more begging for a lane\n[02:22.96]No more hiding all the vision\n[02:24.16]No more making joy feel shame\n[02:25.92]They laughed when the tools came out\n[02:27.68]Said it ain’t real when the new wave sprout\n[02:30.32]But I built with the sparks, built with the scars\n[02:33.20]Built with the bass and I aimed at stars\n[02:35.60]Tú tiras sombra, yo la vuelvo sol\n[02:38.08]Tú tiras piedra, yo construyo control\n[02:40.80]You can call it fake, I call it free\n[02:42.88]I came from the void, now the gold is me\n[02:45.60]No necesito tu corona\n[02:48.16]No necesito tu gate\n[02:50.56]No necesito tu duda\n[02:53.36]No cargo tu weight\n[02:54.68]Have your joy but keep your spirit\n[02:57.44]Toca el fuego, keep your name\n[02:59.84]Taste the world but don’t disappear in it\n[03:02.32]Pleasure don’t have to become pain\n[03:04.80]Pasa el plato, pass forgiveness\n[03:31.84]Raise your glass and bless the air\n[03:34.40]Estamos aquí un minuto\n[03:35.68]Build the life you want while you’re here\n[03:38.50]Venimos del void\n[03:39.09]Now we turn it into gold\n[03:40.16]Oro en el pecho\n[03:41.12]Gold in the soul\n[03:43.12]Built from the pressure\n[03:43.84]Raised by the cold\n[03:44.32]Venimos del void\n[03:44.32]Now we turn it into gold\n[03:44.32]¡Oro!\n[03:44.32]But we aiming past gold!\n[03:44.32]¡Oro!\n[03:44.32]Que lo sepa todo el mundo!\n[03:44.32]Oh-oh, déjalo arder\n[03:44.32]Oh-oh, déjalo ver\n[03:44.32]Oh-oh, mírame crecer\n[03:44.32]Venimos del void\n[03:44.32]Now we turn it into gold\n[03:44.32]Escucha.\n[03:44.32]No tienes que contestar cada alarma.\n[03:46.32]No tienes que cargar cada fantasma.\n[03:48.32]No tienes que quedarte pequeño\n[03:51.36]porque te conocieron en la oscuridad.\n[03:54.48]Some nights are for healing.\n[03:56.48]Some nights are for hands in the air.\n[03:58.80]Pero algunas noches…\n[03:59.68]algunas noches tú mismo construyes la corona.\n[04:04.56]¿Quién te hizo?\n[04:05.04]¡La presión!\n[04:06.80]¿Quién te crió?\n[04:07.04]¡La lección!\n[04:09.20]¿Quién dudó?\n[04:09.68]¡Un montón!\n[04:11.68]¿Quién brilla?\n[04:12.00]¡El corazón!\n[04:12.16]Mind go quiet\n[04:13.68]Heart go wide\n[04:13.68]Tambor rolling\n[04:17.92]Fire inside\n[04:18.48]Mente clara\n[04:20.48]Alma alive\n[04:20.56]Este verano\n[04:21.46]We still alive\n[04:22.56]I’m not just gold, soy fuego con memoria\n[04:27.92]Every loss melted down into gloria\n[04:30.00]Every no got folded in steel\n[04:32.80]Every scar turned proof I’m real\n[04:34.88]Gold can bend, gold can shine\n[04:36.88]But I want worth they can’t define\n[04:39.12]Más alto que prendas, más alto que rings\n[04:41.84]Higher than price, higher than kings\n[04:44.48]Del vacío al fuego\n[04:46.96]Del fuego al molde\n[04:49.44]Del molde al brillo\n[04:52.00]Del brillo past gold\n[04:56.32]Venimos del void\n[04:57.28]Now we turn it into gold\n[04:59.20]Oro en el pecho\n[04:59.58]Gold in the soul\n[05:00.16]Built from the pressure\n[05:01.84]Raised by the cold\n[05:02.88]Venimos del void\n[05:03.76]Now we turn it into gold\n[05:04.80]¡Oro!\n[05:05.21]But we aiming past gold!\n[05:06.64]¡Oro!\n[05:08.08]Que lo sepa todo el mundo!\n[05:09.36]Más alto que oro\n[05:12.16]Más alto que fear\n[05:14.24]Higher than what they said we were\n[05:17.60]Todavía aquí\n[05:19.36]Ay ya ya\n[05:20.64]Estamos afuera now\n[05:24.24]Ay ya ya\n[05:24.24]Feet on the ground\n[05:24.80]Mente clara\n[05:26.32]Heart bold\n[05:27.84]From the void\n[05:28.08]Past the gold\n[05:29.2